item.title: One Messed Up Biblical Family (Genesis 27)
item.description: Is your family perfect? Of course not.Is there someone in your family that rubs you the wrong way? Probably.Everyone can relate to the standout characters in their household, so when reading about a dysfunctional Old Testament family (where everyone is behaving badly) many can relate.In this podcast Dr. Sadaphal will analyze four members of one family (Isaac, Rebekah, Jacob and Esau) and explain that when it comes to the transmission of the covenant promise, everyone is to blame...
